channel.title: Project Controversy
channel.description:
[img]http://i47.tinypic.com/dzzaxz.jpg[/img]
Hello everyone, this is the official release of Project Controversy. If you didn't know I am also known as Gifted I can prove to you I am gifted, contact me at Gifted@ProjectControversy.com.
Server base: Corby Xevolution by Lost Valentino.
Pictures: [img]http://i49.tinypic.com/2gv6cs5.png[/img] [img]http://i45.tinypic.com/svmivl.png[/img] [img]http://i50.tinypic.com/jakylg.png[/img] [img]http://i48.tinypic.com/2lbg6l2.png[/img]
[img]http://img132.imageshack.us/img132/2275/updateditems.png[/img] [img]http://img248.imageshack.us/img248/6015/newdfs.png[/img] [img]http://img687.imageshack.us/img687/267/56047103.png[/img] [img]http://img695.imageshack.us/img695/9223/slay.png[/img] [img]http://www.upload3r.com/serve/060610/1275822135.gif[/img]
Questions:
What have you done to Corby Xevolution?
I've added 474 items, no more customs. I have changed the shops. I have moved around stuff. I have started making construction I have cleaned up the source I have cleaned up the Skill Cape emote method. I have fixed object glitches I have made new stalls I have added new 474 item drops E.G ava's accumulator, Rune Defender, Dragon fire sheild.
Why are you releasing this?
I'm working on a new project now, which will be more advanced Project Controversy was.. say a Experimental, for testing. And to gain some respect for programming :).
Project Controversy server size. Corby Xevolution(base) server size. [img]http://img338.imageshack.us/img338/3521/spaceidone.png[/img]
There is no Anti-Leech go ahead and leech.
Server download: http://adf.ly/430p
Client download: http://adf.ly/430s
Do not post this anywhere on any forum without [b]MY[/b] permission please.
